The '''Tulip''' is a [[Flowers|flower]] that can be [[Crops|grown]] from [[Tulip Bulb]]s in 6 days. 

If grown within proper range of a [[Bee House#Range|Bee House]] (5 squares in any cardinal direction), a Tulip will cause [[Honey|Tulip Honey]] to be produced, increasing the honey base value from {{Price|100}} to {{Price|160}}.

Tulips can be purchased from the [[Traveling Cart]] for {{tprice|30}}.

